Welcome to Palettte!
This app let developers and designers create color palettes easy and quickly.
There are three ways to create a color palette
Using the
color picker
. Full creativity in your hands
Choosing an image
from your camera roll
Taking a picture with your
iPhone or iPad camera
And of course you can export your beautiful palettes as images to share them with the rest of the world.
Create beautiful gradient wallpapers based on your color palettes and save it to your camera roll. Sure it looks nice as your device background image.
Export your palettes colors definition to your device clipboard and paste it into your favorite programming editor.
Palettte let you store 10 color palettes for free. Upgrade with a in-app purchase to store all the palettes you need.
